### Iegūt visas kursa versijas (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūt vienu kursa versiju pēc ID (aizstāj {id} ar reālu UUID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions/{id}
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūt visas versijas pēc kursa ID (aizstāj {courseId} ar reālu UUID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions/by-course/{courseId}
Accept: application/json

###

### Izveidot jaunu kursa versiju (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "versionNumber": 1,
  "slug": "intro-to-java-v1",
  "isArchived": false,
  "isActive": false,
  "approvalDate": "2025-05-10",
  "decisionNumber": "Nr. 25-03",
  "decisionReference": "ITF dome, 2025. gada 10. maijs",
  "course": {
    "id": "aizstāj-ar-esoša-course-id"
  },
  "status": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "academicYear": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "semester": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

###

### Dzēst kursa versiju pēc ID (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/course-versions/{id}
